chat.msg: hey, q tal? empezamos el juego?
Si
estupendo! ahora mismo me encuentro al inicio en el mapa
a la izquierda veo una isla pequeña con un tigre y algunas islas más a su alrededor. ¿cómo debo proceder?
Dale al sur del tigre, abajo de la piedra negra.
listo, ahora estoy justo al sur del tigre y al lado de una piedra negra
¿cuál es mi siguiente movimiento?
Cruca el puente al oeste de la isla
de acuerdo, crucé al oeste de la isla
veo un gran elefante, un árbol y un loro. ¿por dónde sigo ahora?
Dale por arriba del árbol y baja entre el árbol y el elefante al sur.
hecho, bajé entre el elefante y el árbol hasta el sur
estoy viendo una isla con tres rocas. ¿es hacia allí que voy?
Si, cruches las piedras al este de la isla y sigue hasta que estas abajo de la rana.
vale, pasé las tres rocas y ahora estoy debajo de la rana
¿y ahora?
Regresata al testa de la Isla al norte de el árbol.
vale, retrocedí y ahora estoy de nuevo al norte del árbol
Cruca arriba de el cocodrilo hasta que estas al sur de el elefante
de acuerdo, pasé por encima del cocodrilo y ahora estoy al sur del elefante
Cruce las piedras al oeste de la isla y baja por el sur de la girafa
hecho, crucé las piedras al oeste y ahora estoy al sur de la girafa
¿ahora, qué debería hacer?
Cruca el puente al sur de la isla y por encima de la culebra. Sigues al este hasta que llegas a la caja del premio.
listo, pasé por encima de la culebra y seguí hacia el este
¡ahora estoy en la caja del premio! *terminé*
*termine*
¡guay! eso fue divertido, ¡buena guía! *terminado*

chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to play?
Ready
alright, cool! so, you're at the white dog, right? let's kick off by stepping west, crossing the trail towards that florist stand
but don't reach it, just play tricky, u-turn at about 180 degrees, cross the trail again, and head back toward our starting buddy. got it?
Ok got it.
perfect! now let's embark on our next move
from the white dog, cross over the branch southwards and keep going down until you spot another white dog. it's having a picnic!
Ok I'm at the picnic
awesome! now let's swerve a bit
go over the picnic mat, brush past the berry bowl and keep heading west. let me know where you land
Ok now I'm at the log
nice! now, cross that log, heading northwards
watch your step!
I've crossed the bridge
perfect, great job! now, shall we move on?
Yes
fantastic! so from here, go around the bush from the right side and head towards that florist stand, but avoid touching the bush
you got this, right?
Ok I'm at the florist stand
way to go! ready for the next move?
Yes
cool beans! turn left now, go under the stand and head straight till you reach a big bridge with some cyclists
keep going west past the bridge. can you see it?
Ok I'm at the bridge
awesome! now note, just past the bridge, there's a cute elderly couple sitting and enjoying their newspapers, see them?
Yes I see them.
great! now from here, make a gentle move southwards, it's a short walk from the couple and another wooden branch
there's a green bush right there at the end of the branch. meeting point! got it?
Yes I am at the bush
perfect! final stretch now, you excited?
Sure
solid! head east now, walk between the branch and the bush, a few steps should do it
tell me when you're there
Ok I'm there
awesome job my friend! look around, do you see a young brown deer?
Yes it's right in front of me.
fantastic! that's our final spot, my friend
great teamwork! how was the trek?

chat.msg: hey, q tal? empezamos el juego?
Yes lets start
awesome! currently at the tent, facing south
the fire, dog, and mushroom are ahead. where should i move?
Head south but stay between the rock wall on the west and the dog until you get to the dirt trail.
cool, walking south now
oh, i see the car and the telescope. do i continue on the dirt trail?
No you have to go between the dog and the campfire and head north of the fire.
gotcha! heading north of the fire now
Then he'd between the fire and the mushrooms until you get to the car on the dirt path.
roger that! moving between the fire and the mushrooms till i reach the car
Now go back west on the trail and then follow it south to the telescope.
okay, going west and then following the trail south to the telescope
Go around the east side of the telescope but then head between it and the bush directly beside it until you hit the dirt path again.
alright, going east around the telescope, and then between it and the bush till i hit the dirt path
Go west and then cross the rock path to get to the cabin and we are done.
heading west now and crossing the rock path to the house
and *finished*! that was fun, pal!

chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to go?
I am ready
nice! let's start
go southwest under the first palm tree, then take a sharp right at the second tree
Ok now where
swing a left before hitting the third palm tree and head down south, you got this!
Ok I'm on the beach now
great job! spot the cute brown puppy on your left and veer slightly to its left, then go right, heading south
you're getting the hang of it!
Ok I'm south of the dog
perfect, you see a big rock and a small rock ahead? navigate between them and you'll find yourself at the ocean
Ok I'm at the ocean
neat! now, straight to the water, don't be shy
turn right when you spot the big red crab and follow the big rock, going westward. just another beach day, right?
Ok now what
rock on! see a medium rock while cruising in the water? after going along it, beware the shark and go hard right
keep it up champ!
Ok I'm at the shark. now what
swell, now back to the land
squeeze between the medium rock and a ball (it's blue, yellow, and white). press on north!
Ok I've made it
awesome sauce! now, look slightly left and head northwest
you'll go between a red tent and a wicked big speaker
Ok I'm between the speaker and the tent.
party on! now curve around the tent in a sweet arc and then slide south towards the sea
Ok now what
hold up there! before the shore, turn right and go below a red kayak
let's avoid getting wet again, shall we?
Ok I'm there
brilliant! now, make a hard right, stick to the kayak until you meet a cute lil green bush
you made it!
